title: In the room - Extended Version
description: In the room - Extended Version is a collection of 22 ambient sci-fi tracks. Tracks vary from a few seconds to more than a minute to fit various scenes in a video game.
longDescription:
Collection of cosmic atmospheres and more... What's behind the door?

Interweaving of futuristic sounds that express a feeling of tension and suspense for scenes in fantasy video games.

The tracks travel between ambient music, dark music, tension music and horror music.


Preview Links https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XffsZJmDZqg&t=1069s
